Package: scHiCcompare
Title: Differential Analysis of Single-cell Hi-C Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("My", "Nguyen", , "nguyenm21@vcu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-1118-7085"))
Description: This package provides functions for differential chromatin interaction analysis
    between two single-cell Hi-C data groups, including imputation, normalization, and 
    differential analysis. It includes pooling techniques for imputation, 
    as well as methods to normalize and test for differential interactions.
